pageContext.description: A label is marked "Ireland", Robinson Collection". Slight flanges & stop ridge. Ornamented below the stop with two vertical grooves enclosed by two ridges, each of which runs to the round bevel which is marked out in the same way - two ridges enclosing a groove. All the ornamentation is very shallow & faint. The sides are decorated with fluted rope pattern which disappears towards the butt.
